183
00:07:54,891 --> 00:07:55,600
Sir!

184
00:07:55,766 --> 00:07:56,434
Yana!

185
00:07:56,435 --> 00:07:57,684
You need to stop!

186
00:07:57,685 --> 00:07:59,187
You’re not allowed inside!

187
00:08:00,897 --> 00:08:03,274
