to survive—for Amelie.

199
00:08:29,550 --> 00:08:30,343
Okay.

200
00:08:30,344 --> 00:08:31,344
She needs you, okay?

201
00:08:31,345 --> 00:08:32,552
So stay here.

202
00:08:32,553 --> 00:08:34,137
I will talk to Uncle Leonard.

203
00:08:34,138 --> 00:08:34,597
