229
00:09:43,165 --> 00:09:43,708
[SCOFFS]

230
00:09:43,874 --> 00:09:44,542
Liv.

231
00:09:45,710 --> 00:09:47,294
You may look it.

232
00:09:47,295 --> 00:09:49,130
You may sound like one.

233
00:09:49,714 --> 00:09:51,173
But you’re not innocent.

234
00:09:51,674 --> 00:09:52,717
Is that it?

235
00:09:53,259 --> 00:09:55,094
All you want is to cause trouble?

236
00:09:55,595 --> 00:09:56,095
Huh?

237
00:09:56,721 --> 00:09:59,724
