238
00:09:59,765 --> 00:10:00,516
[SCOFFS]

239
00:10:01,350 --> 00:10:02,476
You did it, Liv.

240
00:10:03,477 --> 00:10:05,396
You killed my son.

241
00:10:06,230 --> 00:10:07,773
The investigator told me.

242
00:10:08,190 --> 00:10:08,983
He told me everything.

243
00:10:08,984 --> 00:10:09,984
So I know everything.

244
00:10:10,568 --> 00:10:11,818
Those friends of yours,

245
00:10:11,819 --> 00:10:13,070
