248
00:10:17,658 --> 00:10:18,200
Hmm?

249
00:10:18,868 --> 00:10:19,619
Yana!

250
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:21,286
- [LIV] Don’t try hurting them!
- [LEONARD] Sugar!

251
00:10:21,287 --> 00:10:23,039
