270
00:11:03,329 --> 00:11:04,497
Your own blood.

271
00:11:05,247 --> 00:11:06,415
My God.

272
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:10,920
You’re so disgusting!

273
00:11:11,545 --> 00:11:14,048
